{"tid":1846651,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！！有內地男子在香港醫院扮暈低","createTime":"2020-01-27T16:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T08:37:28.000Z","uid":216555,"like":182,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"dc500bf6228a2cd394790bd2d7f9991ae51f2b08","tid":1846651,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/18fj41hdhTZWlN7S\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F18fj41hdhTZWlN7S&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5sLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=c3a97f4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/18fj41hdhTZWlN7S</a><br />\n森仔接獲前線醫護報料，<br />\n希望大家睇清楚，<br />\n到底林鄭政府如何將我哋嘅醫護人員<br />\n置於險地。<br />\n<br />\n//有個去完開平<br />\n操普通話既香港身分證持有人<br />\n入左瑪嘉烈內科<br />\n發高燒、有精神病史、情緒不穩，<br />\n懷疑但未證實是否患有武漢肺炎<br />\n收左佢入隔離房間 <br />\n但房間為正氣壓，曾要求轉為負壓房被拒<br />\n**該懷疑個案患者沒有被隔離**<br />\n**化驗結果未出就想逃走**<br />\n病人係咁行出去護士站坐員工凳，<br />\n又除自己口罩，又換哂衫想走咁。<br />\n同事叫IC 綁佢，跟住個IC 唔係好肯，<br />\n跟住病人就自己訓左係地話你綁啦你綁啦。<br />\n但番工既同事大部分都係女人，<br />\n冇人夠膽行埋去，驚比佢襲擊。<br />\n所以叫保安上黎幫手。<br />\n若果中左positive，<br />\n就要全ward隔離// <br />\n<br />\n拯救醫護，刻不容緩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r0FxdDf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr0FxdDf.png&h=f212d89a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a5ed3dd8dfd92d9374fbfb89b9125715e152979","tid":1846651,"uid":308233,"like":267,"dislike":1,"score":266,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:48:17.000Z","msg":"唔罷工就係咁<br />\n繼續放大陸人落嚟<br />\n你地繼續醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c704bf162487a05ed602574e1873e97c66c7dff5","tid":1846651,"uid":77740,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:51:17.000Z","msg":"屌 林鄭係咪想滅絕香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8388e6c5b43ee6d382e5b3effffb29e3b1bef213","tid":1846651,"uid":296369,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"叫popo 搞掂佢⋯⋯"},{"pid":